        "q": "What is the minimum number of days to rent?",
        "a": "Minimum rental is two days (48 hours) and is reserved with one day rental."
      },
      {
        "q": "What requirements must I meet to rent a vehicle?",
        "a": "Age: 21 years old. Valid driver's license. ID or passport (if foreign). Damage deposit according to vehicle. Flight confirmation if visiting as a tourist."
      },
      {
        "q": "Can I pay for the rental with any payment method?",
        "a": "Yes. You can pay in cash (USD, DOP or EUR), by card (Visa, Mastercard, Azul) or bank transfer. We accept the main payment methods for your convenience."
      },
      {
        "q": "How long until I get my damage deposit back?",
        "a": "The deposit is returned 8 business days after final vehicle return, once possible fines or photo detections (traffic light, speed, etc.) have been verified."
      },
      {
        "q": "Does the price include taxes and other charges?",
        "a": "The rate includes the base rental value. Additional charges may apply depending on the length of service and specific conditions (additional insurance, extra driver, etc.)."
